<br>
Frostbringers go for about 10-15k, with windblades going for 60k or so on my server, so my question is.. would it be worth it to pick up a FB, or is there something at that same price I should look into.<br>
<br>
My Magelo is up to date, so you'll be able to tell that I try and select my gear carefully.<br>
<br>
Thanks for your input. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=198804">Impudent Blasphemy</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
