<br>
It's not a DISGRACEFUL combination, but any reasonably well equipt monk is going to make you look bad.<br>
<br>
I'm a huge fan of the 2hander.<br>
<br>
Yes, a FB is worth it if you will be MT, but I'd suggest another weapon to go with it as well.  Maybe a Seb Croaking Dirk, or something else in the 10/20 line? Club of the Ice Ocean?<br>
<br>
Yes, a Stone Axe of Dismay will give you the same boost. (Check the Windblade market on your server and see if you want to make that sort of power jump).<br>
<br>
I'd also check into how much old dwarven cultural goes for on your server.  Check the bazaar for &quot;dwarven plate&quot;.  Most servers it's around 1-2k for a BP that'll beat that dusty.  Ditto for mask.  Or, if you are more willing to drop some cash, check your server forum on eqtraders for dwarves that do brellium wrists. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=demolishionglobal>Demolishion global</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(11/14/02 8:02:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4401.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Small amount of advice please</span><hr size=1> go for the frosty = )<br>
